data.description: A beautiful spacious 4 Bedroom / 3 Full Baths on a 77 acre lot. The interior features granite countertops, and hardwood flooring in the great room and kitchen. Make the basement your own with a man cave, play room, office, or bedroom. Located in a wonderful area of Clemmons and close to numerous amenities. FULL HOME WARRANTY PROVIDED WITH AN ACCEPTABLE OFFER.
